## Get a Specific loans 

 

```shell
curl "http://example.com/api/loans/2" \
  -H "Authorization: meowmeowmeow"
``` 

> The above command returns JSON structured like this:

```json
{
  "id": 2,
  "name": "Max",
  "breed": "unknown",
  "fluffiness": 5,
  "cuteness": 10
}
```

This endpoint retrieves a specific loans.

